                <h1>Discover the Salish Tribe: Culture, History & Heritage</h1>
                <p>The Salish Tribe, indigenous to the Pacific Northwest, is known for its rich cultural heritage and traditional practices. They have a deep connection to nature, relying on fishing, hunting, and gathering for sustenance. Their vibrant art, oral traditions, and spiritual beliefs showcase their history and identity within the larger Native American community.</p>
